This is a version of the S2Hat package developed by
Radek Stompor (APC, France); Mikolaj Szydlarski (INRIA, France;
ANR-MIDAS'09); and Laura Grigori (INRIA, France), with
other contributors.  It is distributed under the GNU
General Public License (GPL), unclear which version
(link is broken) but apparently v2 with permission given to use
"either version 2 of the License, or (at your option) any
later version."  The S2Hat package is hosted at and
distributed through the following web page:
http://www.apc.univ-paris7.fr/APC_CS/Recherche/Adamis/MIDAS09/software/s2hat/s2hat.html

The code included here is v2.55 beta from 30 April 2012.
This was the current version downloaded in Nov 2015.

The build scripts using GNU development tools have been
added by R. W. Ogburn, Nov. 2015.
